ind tips on how to drive fewer miles through techniques such as carpooling and local shopping finally the third strategy looks at ways to stop driving altogether such as walking riding public transit and telecommuting we hope these ideas send you on the road to a more sustainable future fun facts for each section check here for additional fun information tips and quirky facts stanford university school of earth sciences stanford university home school of earth sciences home
